org.radix.serialization2.client

Class CollectionScanningSerializerIds

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.radix.serialization2.ClassScanningSerializerIds
      • org.radix.serialization2.client.CollectionScanningSerializerIds
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SerializerIds

    public final class CollectionScanningSerializerIds
extends ClassScanningSerializerIds
    Class that maintains a map of serializer IDs to Class<?> objects, and vice versa, for all serializable classes in the core system.

    This SerializerIds operates by scanning a supplied Collection of classes.
